    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolute gold to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and drives like a dream\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable car without the brand-new price tag. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so you can just hop in and go! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin. Can't wait to see it go to a great new home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available now is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six with its signature individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This example boasts a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis remains taut with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed bushings, while the suspension utilizes its original MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry to provide exceptional lateral grip. Recent VANOS service and valve adjustments ensure the valvetrain operates with factory precision. A driver-focused machine with a clean title and documented service history.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Maintenance up to date.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
