      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my trusty ride and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and ready for its next adventure! Everything runs smoothly, and it looks great too. It's the perfect find for someone who wants a reliable, stylish car without the brand-new price tag. I've taken great care of it, and I'd love for it to go to a good home. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
